<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-14285] Comma at the end of the end of the seed list is interpretated as localhost</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14285</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Seeds: &apos;10.1.20.10,10.1.21.10,10.1.22.10,&apos;&#160; cause a flood of the debug log with messages like this one.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;DEBUG &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;MessagingService-Outgoing-localhost/127.0.0.1-Gossip&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; 2018-02-28 15:53:57,314 OutboundTcpConnection.java:545 - Unable to connect to localhost/&lt;a href=&quot;http://127.0.0.1/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;127.0.0.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This code provide by Nicolas Guyomar provide the reason of the issue.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In SImpleSeedProvider :&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
String[] hosts = &quot;10.1.20.10,10.1.21.10,10.1.22.10,&quot;.split(&quot;,&quot;, -1);&lt;br/&gt;
List&amp;lt;InetAddress&amp;gt; seeds = new ArrayList&amp;lt;InetAddress&amp;gt;(hosts.length);&lt;br/&gt;
for (String host : hosts)&lt;/p&gt;
{
System.out.println(InetAddress.getByName(host.trim()));
}
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
output :&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
/&lt;a href=&quot;http://10.1.20.10/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;10.1.20.10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/&lt;a href=&quot;http://10.1.21.10/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;10.1.21.10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
/&lt;a href=&quot;http://10.1.22.10/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;10.1.22.10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
localhost/&lt;a href=&quot;http://127.0.0.1/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;127.0.0.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
